      "name": "meok-nis2-de-register-mcp",
      "version": "1.0.1",
      "description": "Germany NIS2 BSI registration MCP. Generates BSI-portal-ready (Mein Unternehmenskonto) registration packets for the ~30,000 German Mittelstand orgs in NIS2 scope. Validates org profile, classifies sector + size + entity type per BSIG (NIS2-Umsetzungsgesetz, in force 6 Dec 2025), generates the registration data structure, emits HMAC-signed proof of readiness. Late registration = \u20ac2M fines + management body personal liability under \u00a738b BSIG. Built for the April\u2013May 2026 deadline window. By MEOK AI Labs.",
